Gene set results

Source: R/geneSetResults-methods.R
geneSetResults.Rd

Gene set results

geneSetResults(object, ...)

# S4 method for FGSEAList
geneSetResults(object, DESeqAnalysis, contrast, collection, set)

Arguments

object

Object.
...

Additional arguments.

Value

DataFrame.

Note

Updated 2020-09-21.

Examples

data(fgsea, deseq)
geneSetResults(
    object = fgsea,
    DESeqAnalysis = deseq,
    contrast = "condition_B_vs_A",
    collection = "h",
    set = "HALLMARK_P53_PATHWAY"
)
